{# TITLE: Our Approach #}<p><b>What is a Multi-specialty Group?</b></p>
<p>A multi-specialty group is a cohesive group of physicians, surgeons and healthcare providers who use a team approach for the evaluation and management of medical conditions.</p>
<p>Here are a few of the many ways that Summit Medical Group's approach to care is setting new standards for healthcare in New Jersey, and the nation:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Each patient's lifelong medical record is accessible to all physicians at Summit Medical Group to ensure the highest quality of care for each patient</li>
    <li>Summit Medical Group is pioneering electronic prescriptions to pharmacies</li>
    <li>The more than 100 board-certified doctors make it possible for patients to schedule appointments with more than one physician per visit to conserve time and travel&nbsp;</li>
</ul>